---
<section class="relative pt-40 pb-32 px-8 max-w-[1280px] mx-auto min-h-[700px] flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Soft background radial glow -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 -left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
  
  <div class="z-10 reveal-on-scroll">
    <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-primary"></span>
      <span class="font-geist text-[14px] font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-primary uppercase">Available for Full-Time & Consulting Roles</span>
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="font-geist text-[48px] md:text-[72px] font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.03em] text-gradient mb-8 max-w-4xl">
      Building Scalable Logic with Modern Stacks.
    </h1>
    
    <p class="font-inter text-[16px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.6] text-on-surface-variant max-w-3xl mb-12">
      I am a Full Stack Software Engineer specializing in developing high-performance web applications using React, Node.js, TypeScript, and AWS cloud architectures. Proven track record of optimizing team efficiency through advanced AI workflows, slashing feature delivery times by 75%, and leading migrations for high-traffic platforms serving over 500,000 daily requests.
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
      <a class="bg-primary text-on-primary hover:opacity-90 px-8 py-4 font-geist text-[14px] font-medium tracking-[0.05em] rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-all active:scale-95 shadow-lg shadow-primary/10" href="#projects">
        VIEW PROJECTS <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">arrow_outward</span>
      </a>
      <a class="border border-outline-variant/30 text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-low px-8 py-4 font-geist text-[14px] font-medium tracking-[0.05em] rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-all active:scale-95" href="#stack">
        TECH TOOLKIT
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>
